{"arkId":"cl010156739","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010156739","modified ":"2025-08-25","title":"tess\u00e8re","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"D\u00e9nomination","value":"tess\u00e8re"}],"displayDateCreated":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : Romain Imp\u00e9rial (-63 - 324)","currentLocation":"non expos\u00e9","room":"","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":-63,"endYear":324,"imprecision":"","text":"Romain Imp\u00e9rial","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[],"objectNumber":[{"value":"AO 32520","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Antiquit\u00e9s orientales","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"Pr\u00e9cision sur l\u0027objet : Cette tess\u00e8re de forme particuli\u00e8re nous montre sur la face A un pr\u00eatre allong\u00e9 sous un arc form\u00e9 de deux guirlandes. Il porte la coiffe tronconique habituelle et est v\u00eatu d\u2019une toge. De chaque c\u00f4t\u00e9 de sa t\u00eate ont \u00e9t\u00e9 repr\u00e9sent\u00e9s deux astres radi\u00e9s. En bas les rinceaux se terminent par deux rosaces. Une inscription couvre l\u2019espace entre le pr\u00eatre et l\u2019arc. La face B est orn\u00e9e de guirlandes et de volutes. Au centre, un cachet ovale porte un scorpion, probablement l\u2019animal du dieu Shadrafa. Un autre cachet en dessous repr\u00e9sente vraisemblablement Herm\u00e8s tenant le caduc\u00e9e et une bourse.","inscriptions":"\u00c9criture : \r ; palmyr\u00e9nien\r ; Inscription : \r ; face A : ymlkw mqymw\/qly\u0161 (Iamliku Moq\u00eemu Aqqalish)","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"2,8","displayDimension":"2,8 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Largeur","value":"3","displayDimension":"3 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrec